WEBVTT

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:09.359
How is it, Mom?

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:11.680
Isn't this much more comfortable than eye drops?

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:13.640
Yes, indeed.

00:01:14.079 --> 00:01:16.159
Much more comfortable than eye drops.

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:18.640
It's on.

00:01:20.079 --> 00:01:20.640
Auntie.

00:01:20.920 --> 00:01:21.959
I've made an appointment for you with

00:01:21.959 --> 00:01:23.599
Director Li at Yunhai City Eye Hospital.

00:01:23.599 --> 00:01:25.200
I'll come pick you up in a couple of days.

00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:26.799
We'll go to the hospital for a detailed checkup.

00:01:27.760 --> 00:01:28.640
That's too much trouble.

00:01:28.640 --> 00:01:29.799
It's no trouble at all.

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:31.000
I also heard that

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:32.079
to take care of your eyes,

00:01:32.079 --> 00:01:33.280
you need to look at green trees and grass,

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:34.239
and look into the distance from high places.

00:01:34.239 --> 00:01:37.120
Let's go on an outing to relax in a couple of days.

00:01:38.959 --> 00:01:41.120
Xiao Fan really is a filial child.

00:01:41.280 --> 00:01:44.280
Thinking of taking us hiking to see the scenery.

00:01:44.680 --> 00:01:47.000
Auntie, you raised Ruochu all by yourself.

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:48.040
It must have been so hard.

00:01:48.239 --> 00:01:48.840
From now on,

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:50.920
our days will be happy,

00:01:50.920 --> 00:01:51.959
and lively.

00:01:53.480 --> 00:01:54.200
Thank you.

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:56.200
I've studied this development for a long time.

00:01:56.200 --> 00:01:57.560
The greenery is the best in Luocheng.

00:01:57.840 --> 00:01:59.280
Auntie, you'll definitely be comfortable living here.

00:01:59.560 --> 00:02:01.239
But buying a house is such a big deal.

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:02.239
We should think it over carefully.

00:02:02.239 --> 00:02:04.439
Of these two units, one overlooks South Mountain,

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:06.120
and the other opens up to the garden.

00:02:06.519 --> 00:02:07.040
Pick one.

00:02:07.239 --> 00:02:08.000
I choose...

00:02:08.599 --> 00:02:09.680
Let me tell you,

00:02:09.680 --> 00:02:12.599
with buying a house, you have to act first and report later.

00:02:12.599 --> 00:02:13.400
If you tell them in advance,

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:14.879
they'll fight tooth and nail to stop you.

00:02:14.879 --> 00:02:16.719
Parents are most afraid of their children spending money.

00:02:19.319 --> 00:02:19.879
Auntie.

00:02:20.240 --> 00:02:21.120
You came at just the right time.

00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:21.639
Here,

00:02:21.639 --> 00:02:23.000
look at these two developments.

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:24.000
Which one do you like?

00:02:24.639 --> 00:02:25.599
Xiao Fan,

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:29.080
I didn't raise my daughter to trade her for a house.

00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:30.599
No, Auntie,

00:02:30.639 --> 00:02:31.919
that's not what I meant.

00:02:32.039 --> 00:02:32.719
You've misunderstood.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:34.680
Then you're treating my eyes,

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:35.879
and asking me to choose a house.

00:02:35.879 --> 00:02:36.479
You're...

00:02:36.479 --> 00:02:38.639
I just want to prove to you with actions

00:02:39.639 --> 00:02:41.719
that my love for Ruochu isn't just talk.

00:02:41.719 --> 00:02:43.479
I have the ability to give her a stable home,

00:02:43.479 --> 00:02:45.280
and I will also take good care of the family she loves.

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:48.039
Xiao Fan.

00:02:48.639 --> 00:02:51.439
Life isn't just about houses and money.

00:02:51.599 --> 00:02:52.719
It requires responsibility.

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:54.479
Auntie, to be honest,

00:02:55.319 --> 00:02:57.240
this development isn't the most expensive in Luocheng,

00:02:57.280 --> 00:02:59.120
but the greenery and scenery are definitely the best.

00:02:59.199 --> 00:03:01.039
I'm buying this house for no other reason

00:03:01.439 --> 00:03:03.280
than for you to live comfortably here.

00:03:05.719 --> 00:03:07.000
Auntie isn't trying to make things hard for you.

00:03:07.599 --> 00:03:08.680
It's just that as parents...

00:03:08.680 --> 00:03:09.479
I understand.

00:03:10.319 --> 00:03:12.639
So I'd like to ask you to give me a chance

00:03:14.319 --> 00:03:16.199
to be with Ruochu properly.

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:19.599
Is that okay?

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:24.479
Mom.

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:30.080
Auntie agrees to let you date.

00:03:36.080 --> 00:03:37.199
But as for the future,

00:03:37.639 --> 00:03:39.000
that depends on you two.

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:43.080
Then take a look, which one do you like?

00:03:45.439 --> 00:03:46.280
You two decide.

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:47.039
You choose.

00:03:52.120 --> 00:03:53.560
When Auntie relented today,

00:03:54.240 --> 00:03:56.319
my palms were sweating the whole time.

00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:58.439
Silly.

00:03:58.879 --> 00:04:00.840
My mom just has a sharp tongue but a soft heart.

00:04:04.439 --> 00:04:05.520
You must be tired today too.

00:04:06.280 --> 00:04:07.120
Rest early.

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:08.800
I'll come find you tomorrow.

00:04:10.199 --> 00:04:10.879
Okay.

00:04:11.479 --> 00:04:12.400
See you tomorrow.

00:04:25.519 --> 00:04:26.199
Chen Fan

00:04:34.160 --> 00:04:34.800
How could it be?

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:37.120
Why did I dream of that car accident again?

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:39.600
Is this matter not over yet?

00:04:46.279 --> 00:04:47.519
Hello, Sister Qiuci.

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:49.319
Ruochu, Ruochu, bad news.

00:04:49.439 --> 00:04:50.480
That Zhou Honghai, he...

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:51.759
What happened to him?

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:53.120
He was released without charge.

00:04:53.560 --> 00:04:54.319
What?

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:57.560
The police said that Longshi driver changed his testimony.

00:04:58.319 --> 00:04:59.079
He admitted

00:04:59.079 --> 00:05:01.120
that he and an accomplice kidnapped Zhou Honghai.

00:05:01.759 --> 00:05:02.319
Anyway,

00:05:02.639 --> 00:05:04.560
now there's even less evidence to charge Zhou Honghai.

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:08.920
But don't worry too much.

00:05:08.920 --> 00:05:11.319
Zhou Honghai is now a priority surveillance target.

00:05:11.519 --> 00:05:14.040
If he dares to make a move, he'll walk right into a trap.

00:05:15.279 --> 00:05:16.720
Longshi saved Zhou Honghai.

00:05:17.279 --> 00:05:18.639
He must be dead set on

00:05:18.639 --> 00:05:19.639
working for Longshi now.

00:05:20.839 --> 00:05:21.839
It's a pity about Wen Jie.

00:05:22.319 --> 00:05:23.920
He became a stepping stone for him to climb up.

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:28.519
Do you guys know?

00:05:28.959 --> 00:05:29.920
Actually, Wen Jie's family...

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:31.839
What about it?

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:34.839
I only found out a few days ago

00:05:34.959 --> 00:05:36.560
when I was helping him sort through his things.

00:05:36.879 --> 00:05:38.399
It turns out his parents passed away early.

00:05:38.600 --> 00:05:40.720
He has a younger sister left in high school.

00:05:41.279 --> 00:05:44.240
He shoulders all her tuition and living expenses alone.

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:46.079
Before, at the internet cafe

00:05:46.079 --> 00:05:47.319
and the club, working day and night...

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:49.920
just to save money for his sister's college.

00:05:55.879 --> 00:05:56.519
Then...

00:05:57.959 --> 00:05:58.759
Then now...

00:05:59.199 --> 00:06:00.160
now that he's in...

00:06:01.079 --> 00:06:01.920
his sister...

00:06:01.920 --> 00:06:03.920
can only stay with a distant relative.

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:06.160
The conditions there are pretty average.

00:06:08.120 --> 00:06:09.120
In a couple of days,

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:11.040
let's go visit his sister on Wen Jie's behalf.

00:06:11.439 --> 00:06:11.800
Yeah.

00:06:15.319 --> 00:06:17.399
This partner of yours is quite capable.

00:06:18.600 --> 00:06:19.839
He's a "former" partner.

00:06:20.079 --> 00:06:21.839
Thanks to you for saving me this time.

00:06:22.240 --> 00:06:24.079
I will remember this kindness forever.

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:26.279
The company doesn't keep idle people.

00:06:26.839 --> 00:06:27.720
I saved you

00:06:27.720 --> 00:06:29.240
because I see the value in you.

00:06:29.639 --> 00:06:30.759
You were Chen Fan's earliest...

00:06:30.759 --> 00:06:32.319
The partner running Extraordinary Tech

00:06:32.519 --> 00:06:35.120
I believe you know him inside out

00:06:36.199 --> 00:06:36.839
Rest assured

00:06:37.199 --> 00:06:38.959
His tactics, his weaknesses

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:40.120
I know them all

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:42.279
That's perfect

00:06:43.160 --> 00:06:44.480
The head of Long Technologies

00:06:44.480 --> 00:06:45.920
has been transferred elsewhere

00:06:46.439 --> 00:06:47.800
Now the position is vacant

00:06:49.720 --> 00:06:52.319
The Group wants you to take over

00:06:52.959 --> 00:06:54.079
R-Really?

00:06:56.920 --> 00:06:58.079
From today on

00:06:58.319 --> 00:07:00.439
you are the General Manager of Long Technologies

00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:03.040
You need to come up with something new, fast

00:07:03.439 --> 00:07:06.920
I want Chen Fan gone from this industry for good

00:07:08.079 --> 00:07:08.920
Understood

00:07:14.839 --> 00:07:16.000
Let's have a meeting

00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:16.879
Everyone, take a good look

00:07:16.879 --> 00:07:17.920
at the document in your hands

00:07:18.040 --> 00:07:19.920
We're not making an ordinary plugin

00:07:20.079 --> 00:07:22.240
but a weapon to change the industry rules

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:22.759
Do you understand?

00:07:22.759 --> 00:07:23.920
Yes, yes, understood

00:07:23.920 --> 00:07:24.879
Familiarize yourselves with it

00:07:28.720 --> 00:07:29.519
Chen Fan

00:07:29.839 --> 00:07:30.720
Liang Shichu

00:07:31.160 --> 00:07:33.240
You looked down on my plan back then

00:07:33.920 --> 00:07:36.240
I'm going to use it to slap you in the face

00:07:40.079 --> 00:07:42.120
Seeing this place bustling puts me at ease

00:07:42.600 --> 00:07:44.480
It seems the game investigation

00:07:44.480 --> 00:07:46.079
and the car accident didn't affect this place

00:07:46.079 --> 00:07:47.000
or the club's business

00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:48.199
We put heart into the early operations

00:07:48.199 --> 00:07:49.079
The foundation is solid

00:07:49.319 --> 00:07:50.839
It won't collapse that easily

00:07:53.040 --> 00:07:55.079
But with the game under investigation

00:07:55.079 --> 00:07:56.720
we're bound to lose some users

00:07:56.839 --> 00:07:59.800
We need to add new characters and modes

00:07:59.800 --> 00:08:01.000
to attract them back

00:08:01.199 --> 00:08:01.600
Yeah

00:08:02.199 --> 00:08:02.920
Oh, right

00:08:04.399 --> 00:08:05.639
For Extraordinary Tech

00:08:05.639 --> 00:08:07.079
it can't just be the two of us

00:08:07.240 --> 00:08:09.399
If you know any skilled

00:08:09.439 --> 00:08:11.600
professionals with integrity

00:08:11.600 --> 00:08:12.680
help recruit them

00:08:13.319 --> 00:08:14.279
Money is not a problem

00:08:14.800 --> 00:08:16.519
When I was active on forums

00:08:16.720 --> 00:08:17.879
I did get to know a few guys

00:08:18.160 --> 00:08:19.519
They're all top-tier experts

00:08:20.079 --> 00:08:21.920
How about we ask them to join?

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:24.720
I trust you to handle it

00:08:38.799 --> 00:08:40.720
Brother Liang, you're really fast.

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:42.320
You recruited everyone in just a few days.

00:08:43.080 --> 00:08:44.600
So next, I'll lead everyone...

00:08:44.879 --> 00:08:45.720
...to go all out.

00:08:46.679 --> 00:08:47.720
I've arranged everything.

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:48.639
Xiao Li,

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:51.200
take over the development of Mecha Shanghai.

00:08:51.600 --> 00:08:52.919
Try to add two or three new levels.

00:08:53.600 --> 00:08:54.039
Old Gao,

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:55.559
watch the antivirus backend.

00:08:55.879 --> 00:08:57.120
Update the virus database in real-time.

00:08:57.879 --> 00:08:58.840
And I'll take Xiao Yang...

00:08:58.840 --> 00:09:01.120
...to focus on developing the new antivirus assistant plugin.

00:09:02.360 --> 00:09:03.759
What kind of crappy plugin is this?

00:09:04.159 --> 00:09:05.320
I've uninstalled it three times already.

00:09:06.200 --> 00:09:07.519
It's still popping things up.

00:09:07.960 --> 00:09:09.080
Now it's popping up ads too.

00:09:10.279 --> 00:09:10.919
Let me see.

00:09:11.120 --> 00:09:11.639
Here.

00:09:17.840 --> 00:09:18.480
Don't worry.

00:09:19.200 --> 00:09:21.480
Let me check the processes for hidden services.

00:09:23.320 --> 00:09:24.759
The registry entries were deleted too.

00:09:26.639 --> 00:09:27.159
Wait,

00:09:27.159 --> 00:09:28.919
does this thing have self-protection functions?

00:09:29.720 --> 00:09:30.480
Deleted, deleted.

00:09:33.519 --> 00:09:34.919
Wait, how did it rebuild itself again?

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:36.440
That's really insidious.

00:09:38.200 --> 00:09:39.639
Dragon Wing Companion.

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:41.600
Brother Liang.

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:41.919
Yeah?

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:43.519
Check who developed this.

00:09:43.759 --> 00:09:44.200
Okay.

00:09:49.039 --> 00:09:51.320
It's Long Technologies.

00:09:51.840 --> 00:09:52.639
Look.

00:09:58.120 --> 00:09:59.080
I really didn't expect...

00:09:59.080 --> 00:10:00.039
...that Long Technologies...

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:02.039
...would actually make Zhou Honghai the person in charge.

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:04.120
Zhou Honghai is a legitimate computer science graduate.

00:10:04.679 --> 00:10:06.000
He started writing code very early on.

00:10:06.120 --> 00:10:07.720
The earliest Assembly and C languages.

00:10:07.720 --> 00:10:08.720
His foundation is solid too.

00:10:09.399 --> 00:10:11.480
He even opened a computer school back home to teach others.

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:13.559
He really knows his stuff technically.

00:10:13.720 --> 00:10:14.519
His skills are fine.

00:10:14.840 --> 00:10:15.679
But his character...

00:10:16.240 --> 00:10:17.679
When we discussed game development back then,

00:10:17.879 --> 00:10:19.000
he was always thinking about monetization...

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:20.120
...and crooked ways to make a profit.

00:10:21.080 --> 00:10:22.120
Now this Dragon Wing Companion...

00:10:22.519 --> 00:10:23.639
...installs secretly and can't be uninstalled.

00:10:24.039 --> 00:10:25.159
It even uses rogue pop-ups.

00:10:25.519 --> 00:10:26.519
It's gone from bad to worse.

00:10:27.159 --> 00:10:27.759
If you ask me,

00:10:28.039 --> 00:10:29.279
this plugin is annoying enough,

00:10:29.720 --> 00:10:31.000
but with the antivirus software...

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:32.480
...and games we're developing,

00:10:32.639 --> 00:10:34.000
...it doesn't conflict for now.

00:10:34.279 --> 00:10:35.000
In my opinion,

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:37.120
let's not get involved.

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:38.240
Save ourselves the trouble.

00:10:39.080 --> 00:10:39.720
No.

00:10:40.240 --> 00:10:41.039
We have to handle this.

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:42.960
If tech developers all learn their way...

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:44.519
...of exploiting loopholes and acting rogue,

00:10:44.519 --> 00:10:46.639
the Chinese internet will eventually become a dump.

00:10:47.600 --> 00:10:49.159
People like us who make legitimate products...

00:10:49.399 --> 00:10:50.519
...will definitely get dragged down too.

00:10:50.840 --> 00:10:51.320
Alright.

00:10:51.679 --> 00:10:52.399
How do you want to do it?

00:10:52.840 --> 00:10:53.480
I'll do it.

00:10:53.960 --> 00:10:54.879
Let me take him on.

00:10:57.480 --> 00:10:59.600
Upgrade the antivirus software to a new version.

00:10:59.799 --> 00:11:02.159
Specifically add a Rogue Plugin Cleanup Module.

00:11:02.159 --> 00:11:04.120
Specifically targeting this kind of undeletable...

00:11:04.120 --> 00:11:05.399
...junk that secretly pops up ads.

00:11:06.080 --> 00:11:07.879
So people can not only delete it completely,

00:11:08.360 --> 00:11:09.639
but also block automatic installation.

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:13.279
Give users the freedom to install and uninstall.